logicLayer

Class SVG

  • java.lang.Object
    • logicLayer.SVG

  • public class SVG
extends Object
    This class is used to build SVGS. this is done by first instantiating a new object of the class, and then adding different elements to that object. Those could be a rectangle with the rct() method, a line with the line() method etc. The SVG can then be generated by using the getSvg() method.
    Author:
    Hupra Laptop
